# Update invoice line details on a draft project-based proforma invoice

_**Applies To:** Lite deployment - deal to proforma invoicing, Project Operations for resource/non-stocked based scenarios_

[!INCLUDE[banner](../includes/banner.md)]

To update an invoice line detail on an existing draft invoice -
1. Select the invoice line 
2. Select Edit
3. Select invoice line detail
4. Make edits

## Editable fields on an invocie line detail
The following OOB fields are allowed to be updated on an Invoice line detail in draft status:
1. Billing type
2. Quantity
3. Price
4. Tax
5. Description
6. External Description


> [!NOTE]
> The feature can be enabled at **Settings** \> **Parameters** \> **Feature control** \> **Enable improvements in invoice creation**.
>
> After the feature is enabled, it can't be disabled.

